        <p>Jab hair loss control mein aa jaaye, tab body ko andar from strengthen karna hai taaof naye hair strong and healthy ugein.</p>

        <h3>Nutrition Overhaul</h3>
        <p>Hair regrowth ke liye body ko extra nutrients chahiye. Ye aifrom samjhein — agar ek kharab building tod ke nayi banani hai, toh zyada raw materials lagenge.</p>

        <p><strong>Protein:</strong> Daily 60-70g protein lein. Eggs, chicken, fish, paneer, dal, soyabean. hair 90% protein hain — without it, regrowth slow hogi. <strong>Iron:</strong> Iron follicles tak oxygen pahunchata hai. Deficiency mein follicles starve ho jaate hain. Palak, beetroot, dates, pomegranate — Vitamin C ke saath lein for better absorption. <strong>Biotin and Zinc:</strong> Keratin production ke liye critical. Almonds, walnuts, pumpkin fromeds, eggs. <strong>Vitamin D:</strong> Follicle cycling ke liye zaroori. 15-20 minutes sunlight daily + supplements if deficient. <strong>Omega-3:</strong> Scalp health and inflammation control. Flaxseeds, walnuts, fish.</p>

